1.0.name: wordpress/dzonia-lite
1.0.description: The Website built using Dzonia Theme is supereasy to build and is very simplistic in design, the visitors love to see the whole content clearly. Cloriato Theme got several theme options to allow changing and manipulating literally everything in the site. Still the site is very easy to built.
